snippet.title: Monday Night Going In Raw Episode #114 #AmberHeard #BrieLarson #EzraMiller #SnyderCut
snippet.description:
So tonight on Episode #114 we'll be discussing Warner Brother's reluctance to replace to of actors over legal issue; but will AT & T step in and do what they haven't? Then we'll recast the roles FOR Warner Brothers, with our own spin in RECAST THE ROLE! Then we'll be looking at a hit piece by CBR on the 300!! It's all ahead and MUCH MUCH MORE !
